		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just remember that Nintendo 64 emulation right now is pretty much one giant hack. When its properly emulated (emulating all the various CPUs and other hardware), the system requirements will probably go up vs what it is right now for the current "HLE" emulators.

		

		</td>
